Introduction
------------

This script installs FatFree CRM (http://www.fatfreecrm.com/) on a fresh
EC2 instance running Ubuntu 10.04 Lucid AMI ID ami-6006f309 (x86_64).

You can spin up an EC2 Ubuntu instance as described here:
    https://help.ubuntu.com/community/EC2StartersGuide
When invoking 'ec2-run-instance', use the AMI ID above.

Usage
-----

Login via SSH as the 'ubuntu' user 

  $ sudo ./ffcrm-install.sh






